on, England||rowspan=2 align=center|37||rowspan=2|{{fb|Egypt}}||align=center|1\u20131||rowspan=2 align=center|3\u20131||rowspan=2|[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]||rowspan=2 align=center|<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=England 3\u20131 Egypt |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8545630.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=3 March 2010 |accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|20\n|align=center|3\u20131\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|21\n|24 May 2010||[[Wembley Stadium]], London, England||align=center|38||{{fb|Mexico}}||align=center|2\u20130||align=center|3\u20131||[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]||align=center|<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=England 3\u20131 Mexico |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2010/8699042.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=24 May 2010 |accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|22\n|17 November 2010||[[Wembley Stadium]], London, England||align=center|42||{{fb|France}}||align=center|1\u20132||align=center|1\u20132||[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]||align=center|<ref name=France>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=England 1\u20132 France |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/9194622.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=17 November 2010 |accessdate=12 September 2016}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Norwich City'''\n*[[Football League First Division]]: [[2003\u201304 Football League First Division|2003\u201304]]<ref name=Hugman1011/>\n\n'''Liverpool'''\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[2005\u201306 FA Cup|2005\u201306]]<ref name=2006FAC/>\n*[[FA Community Shield]]: [[2006 FA Community Shield|2006]]<ref name=2006FACS/>\n*[[UEFA Champions League]] runner-up: [[2006\u201307 UEFA Champions League|2006\u201307]]<ref name=2007UCL/>\n*[[FIFA Club World Championship]] runner-up: [[2005 FIFA Club World Championship|2005]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/footbal